The system must be capable of managing:
- user roles
	- student: can only read things on the platform unless otherwise permitted by their instructor
	- instructors: can invite/add students to courses. Has the ability to read and write any of their courses
	- maybe a system admin?
- courses
	- course creation
	- course visibility/publication
	- course archivability
- assignments
	- assignment creation
	- assignment visibility/publication
	- assignment submission
	- should have a scaling factor based on course grade weights
- grades
	- should properly show total grade for each student with correct weights applied to each category of assignments
	- read only for students
	- read and write for instructors
-Notification/Inbox Tab
	- Professors will be able to write a notification that's sent to all students
	- Students may only read
